# Deploy Rules (Vercel)

## Target

- **Repo:** github.com/DITreneris/site
- **Live URL:** https://promptanatomy.site
- **Build output:** `dist/` (Vite static SPA)
- **Build command:** `npm run build` (includes `prebuild` → `generate:og`)

## URL policy

| Purpose | Domain |
|---------|--------|
| Canonical, OG, sitemap, WebSite schema | `promptanatomy.site` |
| Organization HQ, platform CTAs | `promptanatomy.app` |

## Required public assets

- `public/og-image.png` — generated by `scripts/generate-og.mjs` (1200×630)
- `public/creator-janitor.png` — hero figure in ProblemSolution
- `public/favicon.svg`, `public/robots.txt`, `public/sitemap.xml`

## Do not

- Commit `.env` files with secrets
- Point canonical/OG URLs at `promptanatomy.app` for this site
- Skip `npm run build` verification before push
- Add server-side OG routes — static PNG in `public/` only for MVP
